    <!-- ROOFING TYPES -->
    <section>
        <h2>Types of Roof Repair & Replacement We Handle</h2>
        <p>At TK Roofing & Gutters, we repair a variety of roofing types, ensuring your home is well-protected against Northeast Ohio's harsh weather. Our experienced team can handle any roofing material:</p>
        
        <h3>Asphalt Shingles</h3>
        <p>Asphalt shingles are one of the most common roofing materials, known for durability and affordability. We offer comprehensive repair services for asphalt shingles, addressing missing or damaged shingles, leaks, blow-offs, and age-related wear.</p>
        
        <h3>Metal Roofs</h3>
        <p>Metal roofs are lauded for longevity and resilience, lasting 40–70 years with proper maintenance. We diagnose and repair problems specific to metal roofing, including panel sealing, fastener issues, and weather-related damage while preserving strength and aesthetic appeal.</p>
        
        <h3>Flat Roofs</h3>
        <p>Flat roofs offer modern aesthetics and practical benefits. We repair membrane damage, ponding issues, and flashing failures common to flat roof systems, extending their lifespan and improving drainage.</p>
        
        <h3>Slate & Tile Roofs</h3>
        <p>Premium roofing materials require specialized expertise. We repair slate and tile roofs, replacing individual pieces and addressing underlying damage while maintaining the roof's integrity and appearance.</p>
    </section>

